### contact.md (Kontaktseite)
```markdown
---
layout: page
title: Kontakt
permalink: /contact/
---

# Kontaktiere mich

Du hast Fragen oder möchtest mit mir zusammenarbeiten? Kontaktiere mich gerne über einen der folgenden Wege:

- E-Mail: [deine-email@example.com](mailto:deine-email@example.com)
- LinkedIn: [Dein Name](https://www.linkedin.com/in/dein-profil/)
- GitHub: [Dein Username](https://github.com/dein-username)

## Kontaktformular

<form action="https://formspree.io/f/deine-formspree-id" method="POST">
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="name">Name</label>
    <input type="text" name="name" id="name" required>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="email">E-Mail</label>
    <input type="email" name="_replyto" id="email" required>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="message">Nachricht</label>
    <textarea name="message" id="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
  </div>
  
  <button type="submit">Senden</button>
</form>
```

### _layouts/project.html (Layout für Projektseiten)
```html
---
layout: default
---
<article class="project">
  <header class="project-header">
    <h1>{{ page.title }}</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="project-content">
    {{ content }}
  </div>

  <a href="/projects" class="back-button">← Zurück zur Projektübersicht</a>
</article>
```

### assets/css/style.scss (Stylesheet für Anpassungen)
```scss
---
---

@import "minima";

// Grundlegende Stilanpassungen
body {
  font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #333;
}

h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
  font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
}

// Header
.site-header {
  border-top: 5px solid #424242;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  min-height: 55.95px;
  background-color: #f8f8f8;
}

// Projekt-Grid
.project-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  grid-gap: 20px;
  margin: 30px 0;
}

.project-card {
  border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  border-radius: 5px;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.project-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.project-card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 200px;
  object-fit: cover;
}

.project-card h3 {
  padding: 15px 15px 0;
  margin: 0;
}

.project-card p {
  padding: 0 15px 15px;
  margin: 0;
}

// Galerie
.gallery {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  grid-gap: 15px;
  margin: 20px 0;
}

.gallery img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  border-radius: 5px;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.gallery img:hover {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

// Kontaktformular
.form-group {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.form-group label {
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.form-group input,
.form-group textarea {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #ddd;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

button[type="submit"] {
  background-color: #4CAF50;
  color: white;
  padding: 12px 20px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 4px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 16px;
}

button[type="submit"]:hover {
  background-color: #45a049;
}

// Zurück-Button für Projektseiten
.back-button {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding: 10px 15px;
  background-color: #f0f0f0;
  border-radius: 4px;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #333;
}

.back-button:hover {
  background-color: #e0e0e0;
}

// Responsive Design
@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
  .project-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  
  .gallery {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
```

### Gemfile (für lokale Entwicklung)
```ruby
source "https://rubygems.org"

gem "jekyll", "~> 4.2.0"
gem "minima", "~> 2.5"

group :jekyll_plugins do
  gem "jekyll-feed", "~> 0.12"
  gem "jekyll-seo-tag", "~> 2.6"
end

# Windows and JRuby does not include zoneinfo files, so bundle the tzinfo-data gem
# and associated library.
platforms :mingw, :x64_mingw, :mswin, :jruby do
  gem "tzinfo", "~> 1.2"
  gem "tzinfo-data"
end

# Performance-booster for watching directories on Windows
gem "wdm", "~> 0.1.1", :platforms => [:mingw, :x64_mingw, :mswin]
```

